e and defend your Home Island, a strong home gives you power. Visit your friends’ Home Islands and help each other upgrade and defend from enemy raids.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206600/extras/0ab38c595a749c67c4ceef7ad821f5b5.poster.avif?t=1773309473\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206600/extras/0ab38c595a749c67c4ceef7ad821f5b5.webm?t=1773309473\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206600/extras/0ab38c595a749c67c4ceef7ad821f5b5.mp4?t=1773309473\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Fight in reactive, changing environments. Anger the gods and see the islands change before your eyes.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206600/extras/423b7c1e000d5e03ba2d0b6c6f3c3a9b.poster.avif?t=1773309473\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206600/extras/423b7c1e000d5e03ba2d0b6c6f3c3a9b.webm?t=1773309473\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206600/extras/423b7c1e000d5e03ba2d0b6c6f3c3a9b.mp4?t=1773309473\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
